'''El Dakhleya Sporting Club''' ({{lang-ar|نادي الداخلية الرياضي}}), is an [[Egypt]]ian sports club based in [[Abbassia]], [[Cairo Governorate|Cairo]], Egypt. The club is mainly known for its [[Association football|football]] team, which currently plays in the [[Egyptian Premier League]], the highest league in the [[Egyptian football league system]]. The club was promoted to the Egyptian Premier League for the first time in their history during the [[2010–11 Egyptian Second Division|2010–11 season]] of the [[Egyptian Second Division]], after finishing first in their group.

