'''Manta Fútbol Club''' is a [[association football|football]] club based in [[Manta, Ecuador|Manta]] that plays in the [[Ecuadorian Serie B|Serie B]], Ecuador's top-level of professional football. Their rival club is [[LDU Portoviejo]].

==Honours==
*'''[[Ecuadorian Serie A|Serie A]] (7)''': 2003, 2009–14
*'''[[Ecuadorian Serie B|Serie B]] (7)''': 2002, 2004–08, 2015–Present

